ZH: 1. 我竟然忘记了他的电话号码。
EN: I actually forgot his phone number.
ZH: 2. 他竟然吃了一整个蛋糕。
EN: He actually ate a whole cake.
ZH: 3. 她竟然不知道这个消息。
EN: She actually didn't know this news.
ZH: 4. 这个故事竟然是真的。
EN: This story is actually true.
ZH: 5. 他竟然迟到了一个小时。
EN: He actually arrived an hour late.
ZH: 6. 她竟然跟他分手了。
EN: She actually broke up with him.
ZH: 7. 我们竟然赢了比赛。
EN: We actually won the game.
ZH: 8. 他竟然不相信我的话。
EN: He actually didn't believe what I said.
ZH: 9. 这本书竟然很有趣。
EN: This book is actually very interesting.
ZH: 10. 我竟然做错了这个题。
EN: I actually made a mistake on this question.
ZH: 11. 她竟然买了一个新车。
EN: She actually bought a new car.
ZH: 12. 他竟然没有告诉我这个秘密。
EN: He actually didn't tell me this secret.
ZH: 13. 这个电影竟然很搞笑。
EN: This movie is actually very funny.
ZH: 14. 我竟然去了错误的地方。
EN: I actually went to the wrong place.
ZH: 15. 他竟然不想和我一起去旅行。
EN: He actually doesn't want to travel with me.
ZH: 16. 这个问题竟然很容易解答。
EN: This question is actually easy to answer.
ZH: 17. 我竟然被淋湿了。
EN: I actually got wet in the rain.
ZH: 18. 他竟然找到了失散多年的朋友。
EN: He actually found a long-lost friend.
ZH: 19. 这条小狗竟然会做把戏。
EN: This puppy can actually perform tricks.
ZH: 20. 我们竟然在同一天生日。
EN: We actually have the same birthday.
